<bug no-bug="" comments="">
    <id>154</id>
    <title ob="" eb="" sr="">Favorites not updated</title>
    <desc>
        <parg ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1">
            <st ob="x" eb="" sr="" id="1.1">The list of favorites does not (always) show the current state of favorites.</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1.2">Issue reported by Serge Simard.</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1.3">### How to reproduce (on a phone)</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="1.4">1. Add some favorites</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="1.5">2. Go into favorites</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="1.6">3. Select an event</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="1.7">4. In the event details screen: Remove the event from the favorites</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="x" id="1.8">5. Hit BACK button to return to favorites</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1.9">### Expected behavior</st>
            <st ob="" eb="x" sr="" id="1.10">- The event should no longer be displayed in the favorites list.</st>
            <st ob="" eb="" sr="" id="1.11">### Actual behavior</st>
            <st ob="x" eb="" sr="" id="1.12">- The event is still being displayed in the favorites list.</st>
        </parg>
    </desc>
</bug>
